## Relationships

- **Parent**: Hierarchy (milestone → epic → feature → task/bug). Set with `--parent <id>`.
- **Blocking**: Use `--blocking <id>` when THIS issue blocks another (the other issue can't proceed until this is done).
- **Blocked-by**: Use `--blocked-by <id>` when THIS issue is blocked by another (this issue can't proceed until the other is done). **Prefer this when creating dependent work.**

